data.description: Don't miss this! Opportunity awaits with this 3 bedroom (4th upstairs?) starter home w/basement & garage on a corner lot. Large living room, spacious kitchen and 3 bedrooms, and sunroom on the main level. Upstairs holds the possibility of another 1 or 2 bedrooms (currently used as an art studio & sitting area). The sunroom leads to the unfinished basement that is useful for storage, mechanicals and laundry. Doublewide driveway with single car detached garage with remote. Additional shed remains for yard tools. Roof only 5 years young. Previous owner said hardwood floors are under carpet. Beautiful wood trim throughout. This is a great location near shopping, restaurants, churches and schools and less than 2 miles from I-264 (Watterson Expressway).
